  "3001780": {
    "name": "水相",
    "steam_appid": 3001780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/f251c2f9ae369799ed7d36c3fc9719ad.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >水形态</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有跳跃能力，进入清水可恢复生命值，并能在水中自由行动。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e7c48782a8e57261d80e46abbe1b8806.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冰形态</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有滚动能力，在水中自动上浮，可撞碎特殊障碍物、激活机关。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2cef55c9166b6886b53d3487323dacb8.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >汽形态</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拥有飞行能力，但较难操控，碰到固体元素会受伤。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/2c852c60a0b9ed13cbb6400b139e38ee.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >形态变换</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过形态变换来解决障碍，例如汽形态升到高空切换成冰形态下落来撞碎障碍物。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8dca77e06a336dceb206e35c7de38b08.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/3fa1a5bd8f634de6e9b4ae2be6ff7ee9.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >推箱解谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >普通的箱子，多样的用途。它既可以作为跳跃踏板，或按压启动机关，还能遮挡伤害。推箱子可是冰形态的专属技能，别再说它只会滚啦。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e685966349b647a89ad7e595b6b24e44.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >电学解谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >水形态在带电状态下将化身为超人：能通过特殊的玻璃平台、能启动通电机关和计数机关，还能在电场中反转重力、飞檐走壁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/224aacb3e7cb7a254c98ff5afcaca48b.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >光学解谜</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >物理大神小水滴告诉我：为什么水中的鱼看起来比实际要浅？因为光从水斜射入空气中时发生了折射。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/e27edbe6d5699005999f83298389dd0e.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/8d47fb4a6bcbfa8d2967285dba7ee6e7.avif?t=1742206458\" width=604 height=65 /></span>只要简单地编辑和拖动顶点，就可以创作出形态各异的地形，所有平台、障碍物、机关都可以自由摆放，想要挑战高难度的平台跳跃，或者是设计烧脑有趣的谜题，一切皆由你掌控！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前游戏内已经拥有超过2000张玩家自制地图；此外你创作的地图将分享给全球所有PC端和移动端的水相玩家，一起来创造水相世界吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.poster.avif?t=1742206458\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.webm?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3001780/extras/64f18af5ac6f625d139fa711777113da.mp4?t=1742206458\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
